name: FamilyHistoryStatus
title: FamilyHistoryStatus
description: A code that identifies the status of the family history record.

concept.definition: Some health information is known and captured, but not complete - see notes for details.
All available related health information is captured as of the date (and possibly time) when the family member history was taken.
This instance should not have been part of this patient's medical record.
Health information for this family member is unavailable/unknown.
